title: Back-to-Back
description:
Head out for a longer, steady-paced trail run. Focus on maintaining a consistent, comfortable effort throughout the run.

No need to push pace, focus on fueling and positive mindset. Enjoy a low pressure day on the trails.. with tried legs.

This run is key to building the stamina and strength you'll need for your upcoming trail race. Remember to bring hydration and fuel to keep your energy levels stable throughout.
